  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/d922fea1f7af95d9bae41ae5a69a328e.avif?t=1766072157\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>100 Keys To Your Heart is a<strong> sweet puzzle platformer game</strong> where you play a cute key. You must find your way back to your owner, as you open a very important gift. Along the way, you will need to look for other keys to open doors, but you can't take them all with you ! Every key you pick up makes you <strong>heavier </strong>and unable to reach certain areas. <strong>Which one to pick up and when ?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/c97a9a02160355eaaa05e0dc7b7fc2c8.avif?t=1766072157\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Mechanics and controls are <strong>simple</strong>, but they will make for diverse and <strong>challenging puzzles</strong> through multiple environments, each with new mechanics and new keys.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy to pick up<br></li><li>Challenging puzzles<br></li><li>4 Environments to explore<br></li><li>60 Keys to find<br></li><li>8 Secret locations to discover<br></li><li>3 Hours of gameplay</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/052ecd51db224c5444cb39fc838a1d56.webp?t=1766072157\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/052ecd51db224c5444cb39fc838a1d56.poster.avif?t=1766072157\" class=\"bb_img\" width=347 height=70 /></picture></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/d922fea1f7af95d9bae41ae5a69a328e.avif?t=1766072157\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>100 Keys To Your Heart is a<strong> sweet puzzle platformer game</strong> where you play a cute key. You must find your way back to your owner, as you open a very important gift. Along the way, you will need to look for other keys to open doors, but you can't take them all with you ! Every key you pick up makes you <strong>heavier </strong>and unable to reach certain areas. <strong>Which one to pick up and when ?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/c97a9a02160355eaaa05e0dc7b7fc2c8.avif?t=1766072157\" width=616 height=140 /></span><br><br>Mechanics and controls are <strong>simple</strong>, but they will make for diverse and <strong>challenging puzzles</strong> through multiple environments, each with new mechanics and new keys.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy to pick up<br></li><li>Challenging puzzles<br></li><li>4 Environments to explore<br></li><li>60 Keys to find<br></li><li>8 Secret locations to discover<br></li><li>3 Hours of gameplay</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/052ecd51db224c5444cb39fc838a1d56.webp?t=1766072157\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2237350/extras/052ecd51db224c5444cb39fc838a1d56.poster.avif?t=1766072157\" class=\"bb_img\" width=347 height=70 /></picture></span>",
